## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **PAMORA class 2008-2017 (methylnaltrexone Relistor 2008 + naloxegol Movantik 2014 + naldemedine Symproic 2017)** = peripheral μ-OR antagonist for opioid-induced constipation, BBB 비통과 → analgesia 보존. quantum-VQE 의 BBB-non-crossing 향상이 hxq-pall-pamora-001 핵심 motivation.
2. **anamorelin Adlumiz JP 2021 first-in-class ghrelin agonist** = NSCLC cachexia 적응증, 일본 단독 승인 (US/EU 미승인 — ROMANA-1/2 OS endpoint 미달). quantum-VQE 의 ghrelin receptor selectivity 향상 path.
3. **Ra-223 dichloride Xofigo 2013** = α-emitter radiopharmaceutical mCRPC 뼈전이 ALSYMPCA RCT OS↑ (median 14.9 vs 11.3 mo). 비-자녀 castration-resistant prostate cancer (cross-cancer).
4. **Lu-177-PSMA-617 Pluvicto 2022** = first PSMA radioligand FDA mCRPC (VISION trial), β-emitter targeted radioligand — quantum-VQE 의 PSMA pocket binding 향상이 next-gen radioligand path.
5. **HOPE-DELIRIUM 2017 (Agar et al JAMA Intern Med)** = haloperidol + risperidone vs placebo terminal delirium RCT, **placebo 우수** 의외 결과 — 임상 controversy. quantum 외부 (clinical RCT 결과).
6. **esketamine Spravato 2019** = first NMDA antag intranasal antidepressant (treatment-resistant depression). 완화의료 cross-link — fast-onset depression + analgesic dual. quantum-VQE 의 NMDA selectivity 향상 path (cross-psychiatric).
7. **olanzapine antiemetic NCCN 권고** = breakthrough CINV 의 multi-receptor (D2 / 5HT2A / 5HT3 / H1 / M1) — quantum-VQE 의 multi-target binding profile 가능.
8. **dronabinol Marinol 1985 + nabilone Cesamet 1985** = first cannabinoid CINV + cachexia, classical drugs. quantum-VQE 의 CB1/CB2 selectivity 향상 path (cross-pain).
9. **buprenorphine sublingual** = partial μ-OR + ceiling effect, 만성 통증 + opioid rotation safer profile. cross-substance_use (OUD treatment) + cross-pain.
10. **ethical scope physician-aided dying** = 11 US states 2026 (OR / WA / CA / CO / HI / NJ / ME / NM / VT / MT / DC), Canada MAID 2016 + 확장 2021. quantum scope 외부 — hexa-bio 는 drug discovery 한정, ethical autonomy 는 사회적 framework.

